ONNX Runtime Web Library Required
===================================

This directory should contain:
  - onnxruntime-web.min.js

Download it using one of these methods:

Method 1: Run the download script
  python download_onnx_web.py

Method 2: Manual download with curl
  curl -L https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/onnxruntime-web@1.16.3/dist/ort.min.js \
    -o static/vendor/onnxruntime-web.min.js

Method 3: Manual download with browser
  1. Visit: https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/onnxruntime-web@1.16.3/dist/ort.min.js
  2. Save as: static/vendor/onnxruntime-web.min.js

The file should be approximately 1-2 MB in size.
